No stride
# mdtest -n 16384 -i 3 -p 10 -d /lustre_0/mdtest.out -F -u 

Stride=2, because, two mdtest threads are running on same client
# mdtest -n 16384 -i 3 -p 10 -d /lustre_0/mdtest.out -F -u -N 2 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

